Package com.ibm.di.UpdateInstaller

Class Fix

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.di.UpdateInstaller.Fix
  • public class Fix
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a single fix. Populated by parsing the .manifest file inside the associated fix file.
